    <li id="q2">Nowadays the average female manager's salary is between ...<list class="answerList"><li><a id="a4">&#xA3;25,000 - &#xA3;29,000.</a></li><li><a id="a5">&#xA3;30,000 - &#xA3;34,000.</a></li><li><a id="a6">&#xA3;35,000 - &#xA3;39,000.</a></li></list></li>
    <p class="linespace"></p>
